右手に東京タワー 俺はその真ん中
on my right hand, Tokyo Tower, and I'm in the very middle!

569
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:52,070
サボり方とか甘え方とか 逃げ方とか言い訳の仕方とか
How to slack off, how to be spoiled,
how to run away, how to make excuses,

570
00:34:52,070 --> 00:34:58,070
やっと覚えてきた 身につけてきた 柔らかい頭
I just finally learned it all, it's imprinted on my head.
