The speed at which wounds heal...

577
00:35:17,418 --> 00:35:20,118
遅くなるばかり
...only gets slower and slower.

578
00:35:20,218 --> 00:35:23,318
他人に期待をしないのが
Not expecting anything from others...

579
00:35:23,318 --> 00:35:25,818
今の俺の強み
...is my strength now.

580
00:35:25,818 --> 00:35:29,118
手負いでも進める距離なら
If it's a distance we can cover even if we struggle,

581
00:35:29,118 --> 00:35:31,118
行く 騙し騙し
we'll keep going, making do as we go.

582
00:35:31,118 --> 00:35:33,618
身の程を知るほどに
The more I learn my place,

583
00:35:33,618 --> 00:35:36,618
胸を張り いつも通り
the more I hold my head high, just like always.

584
00:35:36,618 --> 00:35:39,218
デジタルな世に いい背伸び
But sometimes, stretching ourselves is fine.

585
00:35:39,218 --> 00:35:41,918
やっと「大人気ない」ができる年
We're finally at an age where we can act "childish."

586
00:35:41,918 --> 00:35:44,518
小さな枠組み ただの数字
A small framework is just a number.

587
