あの日の俺が立ち止まる
The version of me from back then stops in his tracks...

590
00:35:51,018 --> 00:35:53,418
ほどにデカく聳え立つ
...before the towering monument.

591
00:35:53,418 --> 00:35:55,318
隅田川にかかる
Crossing over the Sumida River,

592
00:35:55,318 --> 00:35:57,718
勝鬨橋を渡る
I cross the Kachidoki Bridge.

593
00:35:57,718 --> 00:36:00,718
重なるスカイツリー
Overlapping with the Tokyo Skytree...

594
00:36:00,718 --> 00:36:04,118
東京タワーと真ん中の頼りない背中
...and Tokyo Tower, a fragile back in the middle.

595
00:36:04,318 --> 00:36:07,118
サボり方とか 甘え方とか
How to slack off, how to baby ourselves,

596
00:36:07,118 --> 00:36:09,918
逃げ方とか 言い訳の仕方とか
how to run away, how to make excuses...

597
00:36:09,918 --> 00:36:13,118
やっと覚えてきた 身につけてきた
We've finally learned and acquired...

598
00:36:13,118 --> 00:36:15,618
柔らかい頭
...flexible minds.

599
00:36:15,718 --> 00:36:18,118
カッコのつけ方 調子のこき方
How to look cool, how to act cocky,

600
00:36:18,118 --> 00:36:20,618
腹の据え方 いい年のこき方
how to stay resolute, how to act our age...

601
00:36:20,618 --> 00:36:25,618
脂の乗りに乗った 濁った目した だらしない身体
...with our fully ripened, cloudy-eyed, sloppy bodies.

602
00:36:25,918 --> 00:36:28,318
嫌われ方や 慕われ方や
How to be disliked, how to be adored,

603
00:36:28,318 --> 00:36:31,218
叱り方とか 綺麗なぶつかり方
how to scold, how to clash gracefully...

604
