610
00:36:53,618 --> 00:36:55,618
ばかまじめ
[Bakamajime (Damn Serious)]

611
00:36:56,118 --> 00:36:58,318
くだんない話と
All this nonsense...

612
00:36:58,318 --> 00:37:00,618
うざったい貴様と
...and annoying you...

613
00:37:00,618 --> 00:37:03,618
なみなみの日々に注がれてく
...are poured into these overflowing days.

614
00:37:03,618 --> 00:37:06,718
怠いが溢れ出していく
Laziness starts to overflow,

615
00:37:06,718 --> 00:37:08,918
飯がまだ届かない
and my food hasn't arrived yet.

616
00:37:08,918 --> 00:37:11,318
仕事は片付かない
My work isn't done.

617
00:37:11,318 --> 00:37:16,918
うだつの上がらない 毎日にため息ばかり
I'm sighing day by day that I'm not getting anywhere.

618
00:37:16,918 --> 00:37:18,918
でまたド派手にすっころび
And then I fell down again with a bang,

619
00:37:18,918 --> 00:37:21,118
洗い立てのシャツにこぼすコーヒー
coffee spilled on my freshly washed shirt.

620
00:37:21,118 --> 00:37:23,518
前のめりその姿勢だけは褒めて良し
You can praise my posture, always leaning forward,

621
00:37:23,518 --> 00:37:25,918
肩落とす並木通り 増えた柄と差し色に
with my shoulders slumped in the tree-lined road with new patterns and accent colors.

622
00:37:25,918 --> 00:37:29,118
嗚呼 本当嫌になる毎日だ
Ah, I'm really fed up with days like this.

623
00:37:29,118 --> 00:37:31,618
やりたくないことやったって
Even if I do things I don't want to...

624
00:37:31,618 --> 00:37:34,118
嫌々早起きしたって
...or wake up early in the morning against my will...

625
00:37:34,118 --> 00:37:39,118
その分素敵な何かが 訪れるとかそんなわけでもないのにさ
...doesn't mean something wonderful will come to visit.

626
00:37:39,118 --> 00:37:42,118
今日もまた頑張っちゃうよな
But I keep working hard again today.

627
00:37:42,118 --> 00:37:44,918
がむしゃら以外知らないから
I don't know anything but to go recklessly.

628
00:37:44,918 --> 00:37:50,618
不器用で意地っ張りで 馬鹿真面目な僕らに幸あれ
May we who are clumsy, stubborn, and damn serious be blessed!

629
00:37:52,618 --> 00:37:55,418
重くなってきた荷物をちょっと置いて立ち止まり
I put down my heavy luggage and stopped for a moment.

630
00:37:55,418 --> 00:37:58,118
昨日の事なんざ忘れちまえば同じ
It's all the same if you forget about yesterday.

631
