浴びるday light 羽根伸ばし
Relax and unwind in the light of day.

632
00:38:00,418 --> 00:38:03,318
それか月夜にこっそりと吐き出してしまえば良い
Better let it out quietly in the moonlit night.

633
00:38:03,318 --> 00:38:05,618
でもその前にアレとコレの話
But before that, we'll have this and that to talk about.

634
00:38:05,618 --> 00:38:07,918
その為には先ずはソレを片し
First of all, we've got to do it up before we go.

635
00:38:07,918 --> 00:38:10,918
って今は何時？いやその前に
What time is it? Nope, before that...

636
00:38:10,918 --> 00:38:13,318
今日もなんだかんだ騒がしい毎度あり
...it's another noisy day, hey, there you go again.

637
00:38:13,318 --> 00:38:15,618
1ヶ月くらい何にも
For about a month...

638
00:38:15,618 --> 00:38:18,318
考えずだらだらしていたいな
...I want to be lazy without thinking of anything.

639
00:38:18,318 --> 00:38:21,118
ゆっくり休んで遊んで眠っていたいな
I want to rest, have fun, and sleep...

640
00:38:21,118 --> 00:38:24,118
って思う日もあるけれど
...there are days when I wish I could.

641
00:38:24,118 --> 00:38:26,618
やっとここまで来たんだよ
We've finally made it this far.

642
00:38:26,618 --> 00:38:29,118
ここじゃ終われないんだよ
We just can't stop here.

643
00:38:29,118 --> 00:38:31,118
辛い きつい もいつかは
All the hard and painful times...

644
00:38:31,118 --> 00:38:35,118
笑い話にできると信じてるんだ ほら
...will be a laughing matter someday, I believe so.

645
00:38:35,118 --> 00:38:37,518
今日もまた頑張っちゃうからさ
So I keep working hard again today.

646
00:38:37,518 --> 00:38:40,118
がむしゃらに愛を歌うからさ
I'm gonna sing for love with all my heart.

647
00:38:40,118 --> 00:38:42,618
目一杯吸い込んだ空気
Breathing in all the air...

648
00:38:42,618 --> 00:38:45,418
嗚呼 本当素晴らしい毎日だ
Ah, it's really a wonderful day!

649
00:38:45,418 --> 00:38:48,118
やりたくないことやったって
Even if I do things I don't want to...

650
00:38:48,118 --> 00:38:50,618
嫌々早起きしたって
...or wake up early in the morning against my will...

651
00:38:50,618 --> 00:38:53,118
ほんの少しの幸せに
Touching a little bit of happiness...

652
00:38:53,118 --> 00:38:56,118
触れるだけで全部全部ありに思えるんだ
...makes me feel like everything's worth it.

653
00:38:56,118 --> 00:38:58,618
明日もまた頑張ってみようか
Give it a try again tomorrow.

654
00:38:58,618 --> 00:39:01,118
がむしゃらに生きていくんだ
I'm going to live recklessly.

655
00:39:01,118 --> 00:39:06,618
不器用で意地っ張りで 馬鹿真面目な僕らに幸あれ
May we who are clumsy, stubborn, and damn serious be blessed!

656
00:39:06,618 --> 00:39:09,118
do my thing do your thing

657
00:39:09,118 --> 00:39:11,918
肩の力を抜いて柔軟に
Relax your shoulders and be flexible.

658
00:39:11,918 --> 00:39:14,118
do my thing do your thing

659
00:39:14,118 --> 00:39:16,918
あと1ミリ背伸び
Stretch your back a little higher.

660
00:39:16,918 --> 00:39:20,118
嗚呼 本当嫌になっちゃうよな
Ah, I really hate it.

661
00:39:20,118 --> 00:39:22,118
それでも今を生きている
But I'm still alive now.

662
00:39:22,118 --> 00:39:27,618
不器用で意地っ張りで 馬鹿真面目なあなたに幸あれ
May you who are clumsy, stubborn, and damn serious be blessed!

663
