NickelBurnして火つけて
NickelBurn and light a fire

668
00:40:31,593 --> 00:40:34,593
君の心に落とすimagination
An imagination dropped into your heart

669
00:40:34,893 --> 00:40:37,093
ギリギリでフライできず地獄送りさ
Just barely unable to fly, sent straight to hell

670
00:40:37,093 --> 00:40:40,093
君が飛べなかった理由を一つ教えてあろうか
Shall I tell you one reason why you couldn't fly?

671
00:40:40,093 --> 00:40:43,093
それは目の前のプロップスに心揺らぎ近道した結果
It's the result of taking a shortcut, wavering before the props in front of you

672
00:40:43,093 --> 00:40:45,893
誰かの後をつけてるだけだったからさ
Because you were just following in someone else's footsteps

673
00:40:45,893 --> 00:40:48,893
未だわからないか 最初は気づいてた
Do you still not get it? I noticed it from the beginning

674
00:40:48,893 --> 00:40:51,593
知らぬふりして自分の道だと言い聞かせた
Pretending not to know, telling yourself it's your own path

675
00:40:51,593 --> 00:40:54,293
他は騙せない オリジナルを奏でないと
But you can't fool others, you have to play your own original

676
00:40:54,293 --> 00:40:57,093
過去の自分に足を引っ張られて退場
