Alright! And with that, we have them once again! Our anniversary merchandise! Here they are!

1035
00:56:30,164 --> 00:56:37,164
えっ、今回はですね、なんと、うすた京介先生に描き下ろししていただきました！ありがとうございます！
This time, incredibly, Usuta Kyosuke-sensei illustrated these drawings for us! Thank you so much!

1036
00:56:37,164 --> 00:56:39,164
1つずつ見ていきますかね
Shall we take a look at them one by one?

