First up is... YB-2, it's been a while! Yes, our brand YB-2.

1038
00:56:44,364 --> 00:56:49,164
YB-2の、えー、うすた先生バージョンのね、パーカーです
It's a hoodie featuring Usuta-sensei's version of YB-2.

1039
00:56:49,164 --> 00:56:54,364
え、裏面にイラストがくる感じですね。で、胸元にYB-2って入ってて
The illustration is on the back. And it has "YB-2" on the chest.

1040
00:56:54,364 --> 00:56:59,164
