I've noticed quite a few people using sacoches when they come to events like Expo or festivals,

1045
00:57:14,364 --> 00:57:21,164
ころねもサコッシュ出したい！っていうことで、サコッシュも出しました。皆さんぜひ使ってください
so I wanted to release one too! That's why we made it. Please use it!

1046
00:57:21,164 --> 00:57:23,164
続いてこちら
Next is this!

1047
